      <title>油价因中国需求担忧而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-china-demand-worries-2024-03-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中国需求放缓的担忧，周一油价延续上周跌势，但围绕中东和俄罗斯的地缘政治风险挥之不去，限制了跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-fall-china-demand-worries-2024-03-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 01:56:54 GMT</pubDate>
